summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 9260, entitled "An Ordinance providing for the regulation of prices to be charged by any person, firm or corporation, for the handling and transportation of baggage in the City of Seattle, providing for a proper bond, fixing the penalty for violation thereof, and repealing Ordinance No. 7338, entitled: "An Ordinance regulating persons and companies handling and transferring baggage in the City of Seattle, and providing a penalty for any violation thereof", approved October 22, 1901," approved February 10, 1903.
